text.tspan: Specify the process that has been measured or observed
and classify the process if possible. For example surface
runoff (transport process) or migration as a movement
process of organisms. A multi selection in the classification
type is allows. Add the process to the list with the plus button.

Specify the interactions if they are part of the data. These
includes biotica as well as abiotic interactions. You can specify
the name the partners, the direction and the quality of the
interaction. Add a selection to the list with the plus button.
